================================================================================
  QUICK START
================================================================================

1. Read documentation:
   $ cat README.md

2. Deploy security configuration:
   $ kubectl apply -f rbac.yaml
   $ kubectl apply -f pod-security.yaml
   $ kubectl apply -f secrets-management.yaml
   $ kubectl apply -f network-policy.yaml
   $ kubectl apply -f tls-configuration.yaml
   $ kubectl apply -f audit-compliance.yaml

3. Verify deployment:
   $ kubectl get all,networkpolicy,certificate -n spark-system
   $ kubectl get ns spark-system -o jsonpath='{.metadata.labels}'

4. Test with sample application:
   $ kubectl apply -f <spark-application.yaml>
   $ kubectl get sparkapplication -n spark-system

